Example 3d network, code to reproduce is beneath .

a <- read.csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/master/data/2018-11-20/thanksgiving_meals.csv")


b <- a[,sapply(a, function(x) length(unique(x)) < 5)][,4:8] 
b <- cbind.data.frame(id=a$id, b)

b<-reshape2::melt(b,id.vars="id")

b <- b[!is.na(b$value), ]

b$combined <- paste0(b$variable, "-", b$value)
b$id <- as.character(b$id)
q <- list(links = cbind.data.frame(source = b$id,
                        target = b$combined))
q2 <- list(nodes = cbind.data.frame(id = unique(c(b$id, b$combined))))


q <- c(q, q2)
threeNet::threeNet(jsonlite::toJSON(q), controlType = "fly")
